### ==========================================
### 1. CALCULADORA - cursos del estudiante
### ==========================================

### 1.1 Todos los cursos del estudiante con promedios
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/calculator/student/2/courses
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 1.2 Detalle de un curso específico (course_offering + student)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/calculator/course-offering/1/student/2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 1.3 Detalle por matrícula (enrollment)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/calculator/enrollment/3
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ==========================================
### 2. ASSESSMENT TYPES - tipos de evaluación
### ==========================================

### 2.1 Listar todos los tipos
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/assessment-types
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2.2 Obtener un tipo por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/assessment-types/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2.3 Crear un nuevo tipo
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/assessment-types
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Trabajo Grupal",
  "abbreviation": "TG",
  "description": "Evaluación grupal de trabajo colaborativo"
}

### 2.4 Actualizar un tipo
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/assessment-types
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "name": "Examen Escrito",
  "abbreviation": "EE",
  "description": "Evaluación escrita individual"
}

### 2.5 Eliminar un tipo
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/assessment-types/9
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ==========================================
### 3. ASSESSMENTS - evaluaciones del sílabo
### ==========================================

### 3.1 Listar evaluaciones (todas o filtradas por syllabus_id)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/assessments?syllabus_id=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3.2 Obtener una evaluación por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/assessments/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3.3 Crear una nueva evaluación
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/assessments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "syllabus_id": 1,
  "assessment_type_id": 4,
  "code": "TA01",
  "name": "Tarea Académica 1",
  "week_number": 3,
  "weight": 10.0
}

### 4.4 Actualizar una evaluación
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/assessments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "weight": 25.0
}

### 4.5 Eliminar una evaluación
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/assessments/107
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ==========================================
### 5. STUDENT SCORES - notas del estudiante
### ==========================================

### 5.1 Listar notas (todas o filtradas por enrollment_id/assessment_id)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/student-scores?enrollment_id=3
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5.2 Obtener una nota por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/student-scores/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5.3 Crear una nota (upsert: si existe enrollment+assessment, actualiza)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/student-scores
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "enrollment_id": 3,
  "assessment_id": 3,
  "value": 13.5
}

### 5.4 Actualizar una nota por ID
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/student-scores
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "value": 17.0
}

### 5.5 Eliminar una nota
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/student-scores/5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ==========================================
### 6. SELECCIONAR ESPECIALIDAD (setup_carrera)
### ==========================================

### 6.1 Listar todas las carreras
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/careers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6.2 Listar todas las especialidades
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/specialties
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6.3 Listar especialidades filtradas por carrera (carrera_id = 1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/specialties?career_id=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6.4 Guardar configuración de especialidad (estudiante id = 9)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/students/9/setup-career
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "career_id": 1,
  "specialty_ids": [1, 2]
}

### ==========================================
### 7. HORARIO
### ==========================================

### 7.1 Obtener horario de estudiante (estudiante id = 2)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/students/2/schedule
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

